    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>A computer malfunction prevented The Times from processing most pictures on Sunday for yesterday's late editions. The breakdown prevented the use of color photographs, including those of the World Series, on Page A1 and in SportsMonday. The Times regrets the disruption.</p>
      </block>
